Tuna Salad Lettuce Wraps
http://wearychef.com/quick-and-easy-lunch-ideas/
tuna-salad-lettuce-wraps.jpg
These simple lettuce wraps stuffed with tuna salad, avocado, and tomatoes make a perfect, healthy lunch!
Â© The Weary Chef 2013-2016
Author: Andi Gleeson
Ingredients:
5 oz. can of albacore tuna, drained
1 tbsp. dill relish
1 tbsp. reduced-fat mayonnaise
2 tsp. dijon mustard
2 large romaine lettuce leaves
1 roma tomato, diced
1/4 avocado, sliced
freshly ground black pepper

Instructions:
Stir together tuna, relish, mayo, and mustard.
Evenly spread tuna salad down the center of each lettuce leaf, stopping about two inches away from the green, leafy end.
Arrange avocado slices and diced tomatoes over the tuna salad, sprinkle with pepper to taste, and serve immediately.